title: Walk to the Domain or Hop On the Metro! 6 Weeks Free!
posting_body: Six weeks free brings the rent from $2025 down to $1772!

This Outstanding apartment home has so many features and amenities including a full size washer/dryer, outside storage, walk in closet, pantry, patio/balcony, garden tub, hardwood flooring, stainless steel appliances, bbq grills, business center, club house, fitness center, game space, coffee bar with starbucks and tea, outdoor fireplace, infinity hammocks, courtyard with water feature, pet park, wine vault, corking room, library, private cabanas, pool, and much more.
